('136819c1-de13-43b3-9db4-c43862ca571c', 'It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable content of a page when looking at its layout!', 'hero3.png', 'herosec4.png', 'mockuper.png', 'hero4.png', 'hero2.png', 'Advantage of Using Our Apps', 'Our taxi app offers instant booking and real-time ride tracking for a seamless experience. It supports multiple languages and vehicle options, making it convenient for all users. With secure payments and an analytics dashboard, you can manage transactions safely and monitor performance. Additionally, the app is fully customizable with your branding and 24/7 support for smooth operations.Track Your Live Location Stay updated on your drivers location every moment. Ride and Pay', 'Select Vehicle Type', ' Choose the vehicle that fits your needs from budget-friendly rides to premium comfort options. ', 'vehicletype.mp4', 'Track Your Live Location', ' Stay updated on your drivers location every moment.', 'live-tracking.mp4', 'Ride and Pay', ' Enjoy a smooth journey and pay securely using your preferred payment method, including cards, wallets, or cash.', 'payment.mp4', 'Smart Bidding', ' Accept or reject bids effortlessly for complete booking control.', 'bidding.mp4', 'Select Language', 'Access services in your preferred language without barriers. ', 'language.mp4', ' How Does This App Work ', ' Get started in just a few simple steps, Choose your ride, track your driver, and enjoy a smooth, hassle-free journey with Taxi. ', 'User App', 'Driver App', 'Download User App', 'Download the user app from the App Store or Google Play to start booking rides instantly.', 'Book a Ride', 'Enter your pickup and drop location, choose your vehicle, and confirm your ride in seconds.', 'Track Driver', 'Track your driver in real time and get live updates until they arrive.', 'Pay Securely', 'Make secure payments using cards, wallets, or cash with full transaction history.', 'Download Driver App', 'Install the driver app and create your account to start accepting ride requests.', 'Go Online', 'Set your status to online and start receiving nearby ride requests instantly.', 'Accept Rides', 'Review ride details and accept trips that match your availability.', 'Earn Money', 'Complete trips and earn money with transparent fare calculation and weekly payouts.', 'user-img.png', 'driverimg1.png', ' Why Choose Taxi ? ', 'Modern Design', 'We follow clean UI design standards for better user experience.', 'Monthly Updates', 'Regular feature updates to improve performance and stability.', 'Easy Installation', 'Quick setup process for instant app deployment.', '24/7 Support', 'Dedicated support team available round the clock.', 'useimagefinal.png', 'About', 'Our Company', 'aboutus1.png', '  We are passionate about delivering high-quality digital solutions that help businesses grow and succeed. Our expert team focuses on innovation, creativity, and performance to build impactful products.', 'Meet', 'Our CEO', ' Our CEO is a passionate and visionary leader who believes in innovation, quality, and customer satisfaction. With strong experience in this field, he has guided our company to grow with trust and reliability.', 'aboutcompany4.png', ' Download Our App Now', ' Please feel free to download our app on the app store or google play store to evaluate our product. ', 'https://apps.apple.com/in/app/restart-user/id6738924393', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.restart.user', 'https://apps.apple.com/in/app/restart-driver/id6738922638', 'https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.restart.driver', 'restart-user.png', 'restart-driver.png', 'Get In Touch', 'Have a question,It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable.', 'contactvideo.mp4', 'OFFICE ADDRESS', 'Mobility Intelligence It is a long established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable Coimbatore, Tamil Nadu 641035', 'MOBILE', '+91-9876543210', 'MAIL', 'dilip@sangvish.com', 'WEB